# Welcome to Exstatic!

Exstatic is [HexR](https://www.hexr.org/)'s opinionated and SEO friendly Static Site Generator. This is an ongoing project, and there have been no releases - presently, exstatic is unstable and not suitable for production.

# Why Exstatic?

We decided to write Exstatic for a couple of reasons - Markdown is used throughout GitHub, and it's really easy to use, but it's limited in it's support for features. Jekyll, on the other hand, is extremely powerful and extendable, but doesn't support markdown. Our goal in writing exstatic is to be a medley between the simplicity of Markdown and the featurefullness of Jekyll.

